### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@authToken = 

###
### 1. GET SCHOOLS (Authentication step 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/schools?userId=1

###
### 2. LOGIN (Get token - Run this first!)
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

###
### 3. SELECT SCHOOL (After login - gets token from login step)
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/select-school
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "schoolId": 1
}

###
### 4. GET USER PROFILE
###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
